OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,FThe son of an infected blood scandal
OL,8,Fcampaigner who spent his life
OL,9,Fdemanding answers says the conclusion
OL,10,Fof an inquiry is "justice" for his
OL,11,Ffather.
OL,13,FLabelled the "worst treatment disaster
OL,14,Fin the NHS," the saw more than 30,000
OL,15,Fpeople infected with HIV and Hepatitis
OL,16,FC after being treated with
OL,17,Fcontaminated blood products.
