OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,FThe long-awaited report released on
OL,8,FMonday revealed the risks were "well-
OL,9,Fknown" decades before the infected
OL,10,Fblood products were used on patients
OL,11,Fin the UK.
OL,13,FPeter Mossman, from , was being
OL,14,Ftreated for the blood condition
OL,15,Fhaemophilia, when he was infected
OL,16,Fwhile in his 40s.
OL,18,FHe died in 2021, aged 78, after
OL,19,Fspending decades demanding justice for
OL,20,Fvictims affected by the infected blood
OL,21,Fscandal.
