OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,FSince then, his son Gareth Mossman has
OL,8,Ftaken up the fight.
OL,10,FAfter reading the findings from the
OL,11,Fpublic inquiry, Gareth said: "This is
OL,12,Fjustice, the fact that this has all
OL,13,Fbeen brought to light - that is the
OL,14,Fjustice my Dad has always wanted.
OL,16,F"If I could have him back for one day,
OL,17,Fit would be today. He fought so hard
OL,18,Ffor 35 years for a day like today, and
OL,19,Fhim and so many thousands of people
OL,20,Fdidn't get to see that justice."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
