OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,FThe inquiry confirmed his father's
OL,8,Fsuffering was "avoidable" and covered-
OL,9,Fup by the NHS and government.
OL,11,FThe report also found that the risks
OL,12,Faround the blood products were known
OL,13,Fabout decades before most patients
OL,14,Fwere treated.
OL,16,FGareth said: "It makes me so angry,
OL,17,Fnot only did they know the products
OL,18,Fwere at high risk of infection, they
OL,19,Fcovered it up.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
