OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,F"I'm sure if people knew of the risks
OL,8,Fat the time, they probably wouldn't
OL,9,Fhave had them and all of this could
OL,10,Fhave been stopped."
OL,12,FHowever, Gareth wishes it had not
OL,13,Ftaken decades of campaigning for the
OL,14,Fscandal to come to light.
OL,16,FHe said: "There's still a little bit
OL,17,Fof anger that this went on for so
OL,18,Flong. This isn't something the inquiry
OL,19,Fhas just uncovered, this has been
OL,20,Faround for decades.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
