OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,F"You've got to look at the successive
OL,8,Fgovernments who've pushed this back.
OL,9,FThey've lied and they've lied, and it
OL,10,Fisn't just this Government obviously.
OL,12,F"Labour and Conservative governments
OL,13,Fin the last 30 or 40 years have
OL,14,Fcontinued to hide this.
OL,16,F"It shouldn't have taken this long. It
OL,17,Fshouldn't have happened in the first
OL,18,Fplace and it shouldn't have taken this
OL,19,Flong."
