OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,FGareth says the next priority should
OL,8,Fbe getting compensation to victims,
OL,9,Fmany of whom have had to stop working
OL,10,Fdue to their illnesses.
OL,12,FGareth said: "The money isn't going to
OL,13,Fbring people back, but it is an
OL,14,Facknowledgement. These people need to
OL,15,Fbe paid out as soon as possible."
OL,17,FBut for now, Gareth says the report
OL,18,Fprovides him with some closure.
