OL,3,C'My Dad fought so hard for a day like
OL,4,Ctoday': Son of infected blood
OL,5,Ccampaigner
OL,7,FHe said: "Being able to get that
OL,8,Flittle bit of closure, to be able to
OL,9,Fsay 'you know what Dad, you were right
OL,10,Fand well done'. That's emotional.
OL,12,F"My Dad always knew this day would
OL,13,Fcome, he just didn't get to see it."
OL,15,FMr Sunak is expected to issue an
OL,16,Fapology following the publication of
OL,17,Fthe report on Monday, with ministers
OL,18,Fthought to be preparing to set out the
OL,19,Fcompensation package - expected to be
OL,20,Fmore than _10 billion - on Tuesday.
